{
  "episode_id": "2026-06-25",
  "chunks": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "听众朋友大家好，欢迎收听AI每日先锋，今天是2026年6月25日。我是主持人晓晓。",
      "start": 1.0,
      "duration": 8.882,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_001_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_001_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "大家好，我是博文。",
      "start": 10.331,
      "duration": 1.35,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_002_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_002_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "哎博文老师，今天这个日子挺有看点的。DeepMind今天是大动作连连，从AI Agent的安全护栏，到多智能体科研搭档，再到国家层面的全球结盟，一整天下来信息量有点大。",
      "start": 12.178,
      "duration": 15.257,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_003_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_003_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "是啊晓晓，我今天也一直在跟这些新闻。最让我感慨的一点就是——AI真的开始从实验室里走出来，变成社会底层的基础设施了。这已经不是简单的技术升级，而是一个范式的跃迁。",
      "start": 27.888,
      "duration": 14.866,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_004_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_004_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "嗯，这话说到点子上了。哎对了，说到科研搭档这件事，我今天一早就看到Google DeepMind放出了一个大招，他们基于Gemini推出了一个叫Co-Scientist的多智能体系统。",
      "start": 43.159,
      "duration": 14.866,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_005_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_005_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对，这个我也详细看了。",
      "start": 58.458,
      "duration": 1.524,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_006_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_006_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "但我有个疑问啊——现在的AI不都能回答问题、写代码、写文章吗？这个Co-Scientist它跟ChatGPT、跟咱们平时用的聊天助手，有什么本质区别？",
      "start": 60.447,
      "duration": 14.803,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_007_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_007_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "晓晓这个问题问得特别好。其实区别大了去了。以前的AI工具，不管多强大，本质上都是被动的——你问它答，你不给指令它就停在那儿。但Co-Scientist不一样，它是一个主动的参与者。",
      "start": 75.712,
      "duration": 13.864,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_008_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_008_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "哦？主动到什么程度？",
      "start": 90.027,
      "duration": 1.524,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_009_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_009_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "你想啊，传统的科研流程是这样的：科学家提出假设，然后设计实验，收集数据，再分析结果。但Co-Scientist的厉害之处在于——它能主动提出假设，甚至帮你设计实验方案，然后和你一起协作去验证。",
      "start": 92.051,
      "duration": 16.738,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_010_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_010_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "哇，这听起来就有点像一个真正的研究伙伴了。",
      "start": 109.227,
      "duration": 4.267,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_011_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_011_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对，晓晓你这个直觉非常准。它不是工具，它已经变成了科研流程里的一个角色。",
      "start": 113.955,
      "duration": 6.487,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_012_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_012_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "那博文，这背后是什么技术原理啊？是简单的检索增强吗？",
      "start": 120.887,
      "duration": 5.137,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_013_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_013_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哈哈，晓晓你这是要逼我讲技术细节了。",
      "start": 126.498,
      "duration": 3.657,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_014_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_014_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "来吧来吧，反正听众朋友们也都爱听你的硬核解析。",
      "start": 130.582,
      "duration": 4.659,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_015_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_015_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "好的。其实这个Co-Scientist是基于多智能体协作架构的，你可以把它想象成一个研究小组，里面有专门负责检索文献的智能体，有专门负责推理的，有负责生成假设的，它们彼此之间会辩论、会协作。",
      "start": 135.705,
      "duration": 16.781,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_016_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_016_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "嗯，这有点像咱们公司以前的跨部门协作哈。",
      "start": 152.903,
      "duration": 4.397,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_017_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_017_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哈哈，对，但它的效率高多了，因为机器之间不需要开会扯皮，也不用互相客套。",
      "start": 157.736,
      "duration": 6.879,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_018_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_018_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "那这个对学术圈、对普通科研人员影响到底有多大？",
      "start": 165.032,
      "duration": 4.397,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_019_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_019_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "我觉得这是根本性的改变。科学发现的速度会被大幅压缩。以前一个博士生要读几千篇文献才能找到的研究方向，AI可能几个小时就能梳理出来。但这同时也带来一个问题——学术诚信。",
      "start": 169.925,
      "duration": 14.038,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_020_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_020_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "哦，你是说如果AI参与了科研，那论文算谁的？",
      "start": 184.375,
      "duration": 5.094,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_021_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_021_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对啊，这是个非常严肃的问题。如果AI提出了核心假设，甚至设计了关键实验，那它算不算共同作者？这种边界现在是非常模糊的。",
      "start": 189.948,
      "duration": 11.32,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_022_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_022_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "嗯，确实，这可能比技术本身还要难解。",
      "start": 201.7,
      "duration": 4.441,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_023_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_023_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "哎博文，说到AI主动参与决策这件事啊，就不得不提到一个更深层的问题——既然AI越来越自主，那谁来保证它不会失控呢？",
      "start": 206.609,
      "duration": 12.365,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_024_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_024_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "没错，这个话题今天DeepMind也给出了答案。",
      "start": 219.464,
      "duration": 3.701,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_025_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_025_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "对，我看到了一个叫AI Control Roadmap的东西，他们说要给Agent装一个\"免疫系统\"，这个比喻还挺有意思的。",
      "start": 223.642,
      "duration": 8.838,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_026_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_026_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "晓晓，你这产品经理的敏感度果然每次都很灵敏。这个免疫系统的比喻其实非常准确。",
      "start": 232.898,
      "duration": 6.835,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_027_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_027_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "哈哈是吗，那你能不能给听众朋友们翻译翻译？",
      "start": 240.172,
      "duration": 4.397,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_028_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_028_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "好。传统的AI安全防护，主要是给模型加一些规则，比如不能输出有害内容、不能执行危险操作。但这是静态的、被动的。",
      "start": 244.981,
      "duration": 10.188,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_029_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_029_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "嗯，就像咱们以前给家里装的那种老式防盗门，锁上了就不管了。",
      "start": 255.662,
      "duration": 4.441,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_030_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_030_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对，这个比喻很贴切。但现在的Agent不一样了，它有自主行动能力。它可能自己去点链接、自己去操作数据库，甚至自己去下单。",
      "start": 260.512,
      "duration": 10.405,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_031_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_031_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "哇，那确实挺吓人的。",
      "start": 271.404,
      "duration": 1.916,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_032_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_032_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "所以这个AI Control Roadmap的核心理念是——把传统安全防护和实时监控融合起来。Agent每做一个动作，背后都有一套系统在看，它有没有越界、有没有异常行为。",
      "start": 273.762,
      "duration": 13.472,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_033_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_033_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这听起来就像是给一个会自己走路的机器人装了一个GPS加紧急刹车。",
      "start": 287.694,
      "duration": 6.444,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_034_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_034_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哈哈，晓晓你这个比喻简直绝了，意思就是这么个意思。",
      "start": 294.609,
      "duration": 4.31,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_035_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_035_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "那博文，这事紧迫到什么程度啊？",
      "start": 299.331,
      "duration": 2.917,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_036_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_036_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "我觉得非常紧迫。你想想，一个失控的Agent如果在金融领域，它可能自动执行了错误的交易；如果在医疗领域，它可能给出一个错误的诊断建议。这种系统性风险是不可逆的。",
      "start": 302.693,
      "duration": 12.365,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_037_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_037_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "嗯，所以行业标准必须得跟上。",
      "start": 315.513,
      "duration": 2.961,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_038_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_038_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对，这已经不是某个公司能自己解决的事情了，需要整个行业、监管机构一起建立框架。",
      "start": 318.914,
      "duration": 6.182,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_039_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_039_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "哎博文，除了AI自身的安全问题，我还注意到一个很有意思的跨界动态。DeepMind今天和韩国政府达成了合作。",
      "start": 325.574,
      "duration": 9.056,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_040_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_040_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "嗯，这个我也关注了。",
      "start": 335.111,
      "duration": 1.437,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_041_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_041_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这事儿你觉得意味着什么？",
      "start": 336.974,
      "duration": 2.177,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_042_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_042_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "意味着AI的地缘博弈已经进入了实质阶段。你想啊，AI模型的训练需要算力、数据、还有顶尖人才，这些都是国家级资源。一个国家选择跟谁合作，其实就是在押注未来。",
      "start": 339.621,
      "duration": 12.408,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_043_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_043_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
